CONTACT_FORM_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Have a question or ready to trade? We're here to help!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does KeySwap ensure the authenticity of keyboards?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: KeySwap uses a rigorous verification process, including detailed photos, serial number checks, and expert reviews to ensure all keyboards on our platform are authentic and as described.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of keyboards can I buy or sell on KeySwap?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: KeySwap supports a wide range of keyboards, including mechanical, ergonomic, gaming, vintage, and custom-built keyboards. From rare collectibles to popular modern models, we've got it all!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How does the payment and shipping process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: KeySwap acts as a secure intermediary. Buyers pay us, we verify the keyboard's condition upon receipt from the seller, and then we release the payment. We also provide shipping labels and insurance for worry-free transactions.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I trade keyboards instead of buying or selling?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! KeySwap offers a unique trading feature where users can propose keyboard swaps. Our platform helps facilitate fair trades based on keyboard values and user preferences.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about KeySwap
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: KeySwap is a dedicated marketplace for buying, selling, and trading mechanical keyboards, keycaps, switches, and other keyboard accessories.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I list my keyboard for sale?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply create an account, click 'Sell,' and follow the prompts to add photos, description, and pricing for your keyboard. Our user-friendly interface makes listing quick and easy.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, KeySwap uses state-of-the-art encryption and secure payment processing. We also offer buyer and seller protection to ensure safe transactions for all users.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: KeySwap charges a small commission on successful sales. Listing items is free. Check our 'Fees' page for current rates and any promotional offers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I trade keyboards instead of buying or selling?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! KeySwap supports direct trades between users. You can propose trades on listings or use our 'Trade Matchmaking' feature to find potential swap partners.
